        If someone has died and you are holding the printed page, the
        instructions are at <a href="/recover">executorfile.com/recover</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        Otherwise, the <a href="/">home page</a> has everything, or try{' '}
        <a href="/faq">the FAQ</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>
